  "content": "eviewer must produce 10+ lines of substantive feedback with file:line references. Shallow reviews get re-dispatched.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">07 / 09</div>\n</div>\n<!-- SLIDE 8: REVIEW AT DESIGN PHASE -->\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">Not Just Code</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    Reviews Run After<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-cyan\">Design Too</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    The same five lenses review specs before a line of code is written. Fixing a design is minutes. Fixing an implementation is hours.\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Before/After comparison -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    <!-- Code-only review -->\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-red); border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">&#10060;</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-red); margin-bottom: 16px;\">Code-Only Review</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;\">\n        &#8226; Catch bugs after writing them<br>\n        &#8226; Architectural flaws baked in<br>\n        &#8226; Scope creep discovered late<br>\n        &#8226; Fix cost: hours to days\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- Design + Code review -->\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-green); border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">&#9989;</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-green); margin-bottom: 16px;\">Design + Code Review</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;\">\n        &#8226; Catch flaws before coding<br>\n        &#8226; Architecture validated early<br>\n        &#8226; Scope agreed upfront<br>\n        &#8226; Fix cost: minutes\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>",
